OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FGary Glitter has been ordered to pay
OL,8,Fover #500,000 in damages to one of his
OL,9,Fvictims who sued him at the High Court.
OL,11,FThe disgraced pop star - whose real
OL,12,Fname is Paul Gadd - was convicted in
OL,13,F2015 for abusing the woman, along with
OL,14,Ftwo other young people, between 1975
OL,15,Fand 1980. His sentence expires in
OL,16,FFebruary 2031.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, Mrs Justice Tipples said
OL,19,Fthe victim who sued was entitled to
OL,20,Fdamages of #508,800.
