OL,7,FShe continued: "The claimant said that
OL,8,Fshe felt totally ashamed and she would
OL,9,Fscrub herself in the bath daily and
OL,10,Fthis included, on occasion, using a
OL,11,Fpumice stone to 'scrub her face off',
OL,12,Fand she did not care what she looked
OL,13,Flike. The claimant just did not want
OL,14,Fto look like herself.
OL,16,F"She did not tell anyone in her family
OL,17,Fwhat happened to her as she was
OL,18,Fworried that she would bring shame on
OL,19,Fthem all, and she thought her family
OL,20,Fwould not love her any more if they
OL,21,Fknew."
