OL,7,FThe judge determined the six-figure
OL,8,Fsum includes #381,000 in lost earnings
OL,9,Fand #7,800 for future therapy and
OL,10,Ftreatment. She decided the victim
OL,11,Fshould be paid interest on the damages
OL,12,Fof around #84,000.
OL,14,FGlitter did not attend the hearing,
OL,15,Fnor was he represented by a lawyer,
OL,16,Fwith the court told he has not engaged
OL,17,Fwith the civil case.
